&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Achievements: Ranked #33 of 121 game jam entries&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;
  &lt;a href=&#34;aoi_1.png&#34; title=&#34;Sci-Fi Headquarters&#34;&gt;
      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/games/agents/aoi_1_hu_5cd6532e8623e19e.png&#34; alt=&#34;Sci-Fi Headquarters&#34;/&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;
