 &lt;/div&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://xytheria.itch.io/mikas-forest&#34; title=&#34;Project Page&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-badge &#34;&gt;
